title: The Warehouse Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, British, Catering, English
description: Re-opened under change of management May 2013 after brief closure, this is a not-for-profit, community interest company vegetarian cafe located above Friends of the Earth, via staircase, next to the One Earth vegan shop. Offers mostly vegan food with daily specials board, daytime and evening menus. Unlicensed but you could bring your own bottle. Small, simple space. Near the Moor Street Station & Bullring shopping centre in the city center.
